reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Well made and nice looking. The different compartments are perfectly placed and zippers are heavy duty are work easily. There is also a generous drink holder on side. The bag is lightweight and there is a hanging hook built in to hang the bag in the closet-perfect!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a very good bag and a fantastic value for the price. Its largest compartment can fit a couple of paddles and even another one in the next smaller compartment (if you don’t mind that paddle handle sticks out). Room for balls as well. It has enough other compartments for smaller stuff like keys, wallet, phone, etc. The carrying strap is just for over a single shoulder, so won’t work as two shoulder backpack style. However, my wife has that kind and I actually prefer this bag over hers. Also has a hook for hanging on a fence.Can’t speak to it’s durability since I’ve only had it for a month, but noticed another reviewer who said it was holding up after 1.5 years. It’s a good one!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Consistent quality and great storage space
reviews.reviewText: Seems durable and room for paddles, balls, and other workout equipment. Straps easily switch for right vs left shoulder carry. It also contains a nice hook that can be kept in the bag (attached) for hanging on a fence at outdoor facilities. Great value.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great bag for a casual player
reviews.reviewText: Recently started playing pickleball and wanted a bag to carry my gear (paddles, balls, towel, water bottle holder, etc.). This one does exactly what is needed. The extra compartments and the fence hanging hook are nice. Very lightweight. Zippers work nicely. So far (a month into using it) I am happy. Would have rated higher, but thought there was going to be more structure to the bag. It does what I need and I would recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a very nice, well made bag. I like all of the various pockets!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value for the price!
reviews.reviewText: Very well made. Zippers work well and I really like the padded pockets for my phone and sunglasses. Plenty of room for all my pickleball gear. Side pocket for water bottle fits all sizes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 1 1/2 years and still looks like the day I got it….
reviews.reviewText: I bought this bag in July 2022. I play pickleball 5-7 times a week. This bag is perfect - lightweight, roomy, a place for everything, sturdy. It still looks as good as the day I took it out of the box. I’m buying another one for my husband to use!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this bag to hold my wife’s and my paddle. It does that with no problem with room for balls and other accessories. Very durable and well made. Very happy with our purchase.
